AI Log Explorer - Enterprise API Transaction Monitoring System

Project Overview

Build a modern enterprise web application named AI Log Explorer.

The application will allow business users, testers, support engineers, and developers to search API transaction logs using natural language instead of SQL queries.

All API transaction logs are stored in a SQL Server database in a single transaction table.

The AI assistant should understand English questions, convert them into optimized SQL queries, execute them safely, and present the results in an attractive dashboard.

The application should feel like a combination of:

* ChatGPT
* Kibana
* Azure Portal
* Splunk
* Datadog

Use a clean enterprise UI.

